quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tinndinayﾉ擁 e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun: laaﾉ容 dogayﾉ容 ﾉ容n ka maayo, toowirﾉ容 wa pelle."
  42,33,"Si O haajii deeﾆｴingol henndu naﾉ殿y ndu laaﾉ容 ﾉ容n, O waﾉ預y; ndu waﾉ葉ina ontuma, tabitu ndu e hoore maayo ngon. Woni e ko jantaa koo, maandeeji ﾉ殿nnginﾉ擁 kattal Allah ngal, wonannde kala muﾃｱﾃｱotooﾉ熔 jarrabuyee, yettoowo neema Allah on e dow mun."
  42,34,"Si Mo yiﾉ擁 Kanko Allah, O yooliray ﾉ容n laaﾉ容, wurtugol heenndu tiiﾉ蓉ndu e majje, sabu bakkaatu ko yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 e bakkatuuji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n."
  42,35,"Tuma O halkirta laaﾉ容 ﾉ容n henndu ndun, wennjaynooﾉ兎 e Aayeeje Allah ﾉ容n, fii bonnitugol ﾉ容, hiﾉ兎 wonnde ontuma, wonnde alaa no ﾉ兎 laawora e halkaare nden."
  42,36,"Kala huunde nde hokkaﾉ熔n onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, woni ko jaahu maa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, haray ko dakamme nguurndam aduna, ko ko fii mun lannata; neema duumotooﾉ熔 on, ko neema Aljanna on mo Allah marani gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Mo ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ni Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, hara ko e Joomi maﾉ橡兎 tun, woni ﾉ兎 fawotoo e fiyaaku maﾉ橡兎 kala."
  42,37,"ﾆ‘n woﾉ遼擁totooﾉ兎 e junuubi mawﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n e pankare ﾉ容n, si wonii ﾉ兎 tikkanii fawﾃｱoriiﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 konngol maa kuugal, hara ﾉ兎 yaaforay ontigi e ﾉ蓉m, sabu moﾆｴﾆｴere e maslaha ko woni e mun."
  42,38,"ﾆ‘n nootoriiﾉ兎 Joomi maﾉ橡兎, huuwugol ko O yamiri ﾉ兎, woﾉ遼擁too e ko O haﾉ擁 ﾉ兎, ﾃｱiﾉ渡ir ﾉ兎 julde nden no timmiri, ﾉ兎 tawata ko diisondirayﾉ兎 hakkunde maﾉ橡兎, e kala fiyaaku maﾉ橡兎, wintotorayﾉ兎 fii Allah, e kon ko Men arsiki ﾉ兎."
  42,39,"E ﾉ兎n tawﾉ兎 si tooﾃｱe yanii e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 yottoray teddingol hoore maﾉ橡兎, tuma tawi hara tooﾃｱuﾉ熔 on hanndaa e yaafeede. Nden yottannde, ko jojjunde, teﾅ逆inii si nafa alaa e yaafagol ngol."
  42,40,"Kala faalaaﾉ熔 yottaade, ko hakkee makko. Ko woni tun, hara ko yeru mun, ko aldaa e ﾉ兎ydugol maa fantingol. Kala non yaafiiﾉ熔 boniiﾉ熔 e mun, o moﾆｴﾆｴintini hakkunde maﾉ橡兎, haray njoﾉ電i makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiﾉ預a tooﾃｱirooﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ka wonikiiji e ka jawle e guri maﾉ橡兎; Himo aﾃｱi ﾉ兎n."
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiﾉ熔, ko ﾉ兎n woni ﾉ兎 nanngitirtaake ko waﾉ擁 kon."
  42,42,"Ka nanngitireede lepte fawii e mun, ko tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, hara hiﾉ兎 huuwa geddi e leydi ndin: ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n, lepte muusuﾉ容 hino woodani laakara."
  42,43,"Muﾃｱﾃｱiiﾉ熔 on kadi o yaafii tooﾃｱe ﾉ容n, ko pellet, moﾆｴﾆｴere ngal muﾃｱal ﾉ熔n, yiltoto e makko wonndude e renndo ngon. ﾆ隔m ko fiyaaku yettiniiﾉ熔, ko jom-geﾉ殿l mawngal tun, woni ko hawrondirta e ﾉ蓉m."
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah hoyni gaa e peewal haa O majjini ontigi e goonga kan, haray giﾉ熔 goo alanaa mo, mo no heftana mo fiyakuuji makko ﾉ擁n. A tinay tooﾃｱirnooﾉ兎 ko'e mun ﾉ兎n geddi e keeferaaku, tuma ﾉ兎 yi'i lepte ﾉ容n ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, hiﾉ兎 yeloo wi'a: hara laawol ruttorde aduna no woodi, men tuubana Allah?"